<inglise> COUNCIL DECISION of 31 July 1972 setting up a Standing Committee for Agricultural Statistics (72/279/EEC) </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU OTSUS, millega luuakse alalise p&otilde;llumajandusstatistika komitee 31. juuli 1972 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> 72/279/EM&Uuml; EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the draft decision submitted by the Commission; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni esitatud otsuse eeln&otilde;u; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, for the purpose of facilitating their implementation, provision is made in acts adopted by the Council relating to agricultural statistics for a procedure establishing close cooperation between Member States and the Commission; whereas, in order to achieve such cooperation, a Committee should be set up to carry out the duties assigned to it by such acts; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: n&otilde;ukogu poolt vastuv&otilde;etud p&otilde;llumajandusstatistikaaktide s&auml;tetes n&auml;hakse ette nende rakendamise h&otilde;lbustamiseks menetlus liikmesriikide ja komisjoni vahelise tiheda koost&ouml;&ouml; sisseseadmiseks; selle koost&ouml;&ouml; saavutamiseks tuleks luua komitee, kes t&auml;idab talle nende aktidega etten&auml;htud &uuml;lesandeid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is desirable that this Committee should consider any other question arising in connection with such acts, </inglise>
<eesti> on soovitav, et see komitee k&auml;sitleks k&otilde;iki nendest aktidest tulenevaid k&uuml;simusi, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS DECIDED AS FOLLOWS: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD J&Auml;RGMISE OTSUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> A Standing Committee for Agricultural Statistics (hereinafter called the "Committee") is hereby set up; it shall consist of representatives of the Member States with a representative of the Commission as Chairman. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevaga moodustatakse alalise p&otilde;llumajandusstatistika komitee (edaspidi "komitee"), mis koosneb liikmesriikide esindajatest ja mille eesistuja on komisjoni esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall carry out the duties assigned to it by the provisions adopted by the Council in the field of agricultural statistics in the cases and under the conditions provided for therein. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee t&auml;idab talle komisjoni poolt vastuv&otilde;etud p&otilde;llumajandusstatistikaalaste s&auml;tetega etten&auml;htud &uuml;lesandeid nendes s&auml;tetes etten&auml;htud juhtudel ja tingimustel. </eesti>
<inglise> It may, moreover, consider any other question arising in connection with such provisions and referred to it by the Chairman either on his own initiative or at the request of a Member State. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee v&otilde;ib k&auml;sitleda k&otilde;iki nendest s&auml;tetest tulenevaid muid k&uuml;simusi, mis komitee esimees talle omal algatusel v&otilde;i liikmesriigi esindaja taotluse korral suunab. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The Committee shall adopt its own rules of procedure. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee v&otilde;tab vastu oma t&ouml;&ouml;korra. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 31 July 1972. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 31. juuli 1972 </eesti>
<inglise> For the Council </inglise>
<eesti> N&otilde;ukogu nimel </eesti>
<inglise> The President </inglise>
<eesti> eesistuja </eesti>
<inglise> T. WESTERTERP </inglise>
